  "favicon": "https://www.yatzer.com/sites/all/themes/yatzer/images/favicons/apple-touch-icon-180x180.png",
  "text": "Skip to main content Design Architecture Art Fashion City Experiences Agenda Indian Heritage Meets Avant-Garde Design: A Conversation with Vikram GoyalArt Athina 2024: Highlights from Greece's Annual Contemporary Art FairModern Meets Classic: A Studio Apartment in Kraków Masterfully Transformed by Furora StudioReimagining Summer: Studio Bonarchi’s Nostalgic Revival of a Seaside Apartment in GreeceThasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects Photography by Kim Powell. Thasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects LocationDetailed InformationProject NameThasos loftPosted inInterior DesignLocation Thasos Greece Architecture PracticeMinas Kosmidis ArchitectsArea (sqm)150CompletedMay 2024 Located on the Greek island of Thasos, this recently completed summer home for a family of three is a prime example of how modern design can coexist with tradition, evident through Greek practice Minas Kosmidis Architects seamless transformation of an existing stone structure into a modern retreat while preserving its traditional charm. The practice’s signature approach—rooted in clarity of form, symmetry, and transparency—shines through in every detail of the project, as does the architects’ unique talent in harmoniously integrating disparate materials. The result is a loft-like residence that feels both timeless and refreshingly contemporary, its refined minimalism echoing the natural serenity of the island. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. The design focuses on integrating the house with its natural surroundings. The original stone structure has been retained, embodying the timeless beauty of local architecture, while a metal framework, introduced to support the upper level, gives the home a modern edge while maintaining structural integrity. On the ground floor, the open-plan layout emphasizes fluidity and openness. The back houses the staircase and secondary functions, clearing the way for unobstructed sea views from the living area, which acts as the heart of the home. The kitchen, cleverly designed with folding doors, transforms into a sleek wooden box when not in use, maintaining the scheme’s minimalist aesthetic. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Upstairs, the two bedrooms offer privacy without compromising any connection to the home's open design. A glass partition incorporated in the metal framework subtly separates the spaces from the living area below, allowing light to flow through and offering visual continuity. Painted black and fitted with Crittall-style internal windows—a practical way to ensure natural ventilation for the bedrooms in conjunction with skylights—the framework lends subtle industrial vibes. Concrete flooring, contemporary furniture, and a monochromatic palette of white and grey further enhance the space’s loft-like sensation, while the use of natural wood and stone anchor the design in the island’s earthy palette. The juxtaposition of materials—stone, metal, and wood—balances the characteristic rusticity of the island’s architecture with contemporary design, creating a serene yet functional space in what is ultimately a harmonious dialogue between the past and present. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Photography by Kim Powell. Thasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects 1 of Join our mailing list Sign up to receive Yatzer's newsletter and get our latest stories twice a month delivered directly to your mailbox. Adult Content This post contains ad