ostalgic Revival of a Seaside Apartment in Greece\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"368\" height=\"550\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/01_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg?itok=tbJ5WeVi\" alt=\"Thasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects\" title=\"Thasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/01_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg?itok=tbJ5WeVi\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eThasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003csection id=\"main\"\u003e\n  \n  \n\n  \n  \u003csection\u003e\n\n        \n    \n  \n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv id=\"hero\"\u003e    \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003e\n  \u003ch2\u003eThasos Loft: A Harmonious Blend of Tradition and Modernity by Minas Kosmidis Architects\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch5\u003eLocation\u003c/h5\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003cth colspan=\"6\"\u003eDetailed Information\u003c/th\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/thead\u003e\u003ctbody\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eProject Name\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eThasos loft\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003ePosted in\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.yatzer.com/design/interior-design\"\u003eInterior Design\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eLocation\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThasos\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGreece\u003c/span\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eArchitecture Practice\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.yatzer.com/yatzerpedia/minas-kosmidis-architects\"\u003eMinas Kosmidis Architects\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eArea (sqm)\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e150\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eCompleted\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eMay 2024\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e      \u003c/div\u003e\n      \n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \n      \n              \u003cp\u003eLocated on the Greek island of Thasos, this recently completed summer home for a family of three is a prime example of how modern design can coexist with tradition, evident through Greek practice \u003ca href=\"https://minaskosmidis.com/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMinas Kosmidis Architects \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003eseamless transformation of an existing stone structure into a modern retreat while preserving its traditional charm. \u003cstrong\u003eThe practice’s signature approach\u003c/strong\u003e—\u003cstrong\u003erooted in clarity of form, symmetry, and transparency\u003c/strong\u003e—\u003cstrong\u003eshines through in every detail of the project, as does the architects’ unique talent in harmoniously integrating disparate materials.\u003c/strong\u003e The result is a loft-like residence that feels both timeless and refreshingly contemporary, its refined minimalism echoing the natural serenity of the island.\u003c/p\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/13_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1467