003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1807\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/07_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1737\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/11_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eThe design focuses on integrating the house with its natural surroundings. \u003cstrong\u003eThe original stone structure has been retained, embodying the timeless beauty of local architecture, while a metal framework, introduced to support the upper level, gives the home a modern edge while maintaining structural integrity.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOn the ground floor, the open-plan layout emphasizes fluidity and openness. The back houses the staircase and secondary functions, clearing the way for unobstructed sea views from the living area, which acts as the heart of the home. The kitchen, cleverly designed with folding doors, transforms into a sleek wooden box when not in use, maintaining the scheme’s minimalist aesthetic.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2638\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/05_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/02_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/02_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1917\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell