ell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2270\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/15_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2270\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/16_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"2443\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/14_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"2089\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/09_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003eUpstairs, the two bedrooms offer privacy without compromising any connection to the home\u0026#39;s open design. A glass partition incorporated in the metal framework subtly separates the spaces from the living area below, allowing light to flow through and offering visual continuity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePainted black and fitted with Crittall-style internal windows—a practical way to ensure natural ventilation for the bedrooms in conjunction with skylights—the framework lends subtle industrial vibes. \u003cstrong\u003eConcrete flooring, contemporary furniture, and a monochromatic palette of white and grey further enhance the space’s loft-like sensation, while the use of natural wood and stone anchor the design in the island’s earthy palette.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe juxtaposition of materials—stone, metal, and wood—balances the characteristic rusticity of the island’s architecture with contemporary design, creating a serene yet functional space in what is ultimately a harmonious dialogue between the past and present.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1705\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/17_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n  \n      \u003cp\u003ePhotography by Kim Powell.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \n\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cimg data-original-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_thasos_loft_minas_kosmidis_architects_kim_powell_yatzer.jpg\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1795\" alt=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" title=\"Photography by Kim Powell.\" data-src=\"https://www.yatzer.com/sites/default/files/media/slideshow/20_thasos_loft_m